{%- comment -%}
  William Ashford — Custom robots.txt
  Explicit rules only. Does NOT inherit robots.default_groups, which can
  emit a broad "Disallow: /" when the store is password-protected or in
  development mode, effectively blocking all crawlers.

  Rule priority (Google + Bing): longest matching path wins.
  Allow: / + Disallow: /admin → /admin is blocked (longer match), all else is open.
{%- endcomment -%}

